  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The dining room is open for breakfast and dinner and has a lovely menu that showcases the region’s delicious cuisine. The hotel uses locally-sourced products and meals are complemented with some lovely wines. Breakfast is served buffet style with a choice of hot and cold options and for dinner you'll have a choice of four-courses including a salad and vegetable buffet. Once a week there's a Tyrolean themed Gala dinner.</p>
<p>The hotel requests that no shorts or flip-flops be worn at dinner, the dress code is smart-casual.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
