  <facilityDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Val Gardena Active Programme partner accommodation</strong></p>
<p>Hotel Mignon is an affiliate of the <a rel="noopener" href="https://www.valgardena-active.com/en/summer" target="_blank">Val Gardena Active</a> programme so you can join free or discounted activities every day of the week (activities are bookable and payable locally).</p>
<p><strong>Hotel facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>State-of-the-art spa and wellness area with heated indoor pool, sauna, steam bath, whirlpool, fitness room and a relaxation room</li>
<li>Massages, solarium &amp; beauty treatments (payable locally)</li>
<li>Spa and pool towels are provided</li>
<li>South-facing garden</li>
<li>Free Wi-Fi</li>
<li>Parking garage (payable locally)</li>
</ul>]]></facilityDescription>
